{"tid":1804784,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"<出現了!> 黑警破獲武器庫 檢百枚汽油彈  或今明兩日製造混亂","createTime":"2019-12-31T08:45:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T13:08:05.000Z","uid":227801,"like":164,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"36a8a9e455d86320b5488cf0bb149470c5fccb13","tid":1804784,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"都話咗民陣遊行前會出現武器庫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1244631&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1244631%26csid%3D261_341&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=37fa1c30\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1244631&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n警方在黃大仙沙田坳道法藏寺對出檢獲6桶汽油，及51個空玻璃樽。相信是製作汽油彈的原材料，可製成超過100枚汽油彈，可能在今日或明天在公眾活動使用，目的是製造恐慌及混亂。東九龍重案組總督察王爾威指，行動是由警察總部刑事部負責，今早拘捕部分人後，得悉現場存在危險品，東九龍重案組再採取行動，正調查儲存危險品時間。<br />\n王爾威指現場是行山徑，批評涉案人士在現場儲存危險品不負責任，對行山人士及社區構成危險。他反駁有人形容汽油彈內藏有無限「溫柔」，強調汽油彈是攻擊性武器，甚至可視作爆炸品，是犯罪工具，目的只有危害他人生命及安全，當中只存有犯罪元素，呼籲市民，尤其是青年人不要被人利用或煽動，去製造或儲存汽油彈，一旦定罪，最高監禁20年。"},{"pid":"4d5c372fbd1cad43f9ab4a1332e51ea0d6a8ef20","tid":1804784,"uid":317979,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T08:45:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n！最後今日！<br />\n<br />\n德國聯署<br />\n仲差2萬幾人！<br />\n(⌐■-■)(⌐■-■)(⌐■-■)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1804609\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1804609</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=bb330964\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_0